Rewrite the way qcl handles queries based on the concept of a query tree based on triples,
compare the CQL parser at http://www.csc.liv.ac.uk/~azaroth/stuff/, also look at RDF query 
languages and converters between SPARQL and SQL

qcl_data_query_AbstractParser
qcl_data_query_AbstractQuery
qcl_data_query_Triple
qcl_data_query_Relation
qcl_data_query_SearchTerm
qcl_data_query_Predicate

This will make it possible to translate from and to SQL using this query tree.

